    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Rufus Poenino <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>at tua templa l&amp;lt;i=Y&amp;gt;bens vota suscepta pere&amp;lt;g=C&amp;gt;i <lb n="3"/>accepta ut tibi sint numen adoro tuum <lb n="4"/>inpensis <note>sic</note> non ma&amp;lt;g=C&amp;gt;na quidem te sancte precamur <lb n="5"/>maiorem sa<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>culo</abbr></expan> nostrum ani&amp;lt;m=N&amp;gt;um accipias 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tessera in Form einer tabula ansata, bei welcher die ansae auf beiden Seiten fehlen. Die in feinen Buchstaben gepunzte Inschrift enthält in Zeile 2-5 zwei Distichen. (B): AE 1991, Gasperini: Z. 2: voto.</p>
            </div>
